Y29tL2VuLXVzL3Nob3Avcm9hbSIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMTBhMDcxYjMtMzU2Yi00ODMyLWFkMmQtODljNDFiYWNiMzQxIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAYa2siXqoA_OZRSq-F_IJgpvN0ftfKj-gSznH4-DT1LN&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sonos.com%2Fen-us%2Fshop%2Froam" class="rapid-with-clickid">Roam</a>会打折。这两款便携式扬声器都可以让您在户外享受 Sonos 一般稳定的音质，而 Move 是 Roam 的更强大的表亲。 Move 的防护等级为 IP56，而 Roam 的防水等级为 IP67，两者均支持 AirPlay 2、语音命令以及蓝牙和 WiFi 连接。您可以期待 Move 发出更强劲、更响亮的声音，使其成为拥有大后院的人的不错选择，而 Roam 则更适合背包携带。</p><p>如果您渴望获得新的 Era 100 或 300，它们包含在一些打折的家庭影院套装中。最实惠的选择是<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Sonos;elmt:;cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=1e71dc69-0ad7-47e7-abf5-dc3926557fa3&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Sonos&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiIxZTcxZGM2OS0wYWQ3LTQ3ZTctYWJmNS1kYzM5MjY1NTdmYTMiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc29ub3MuY29tL2VuLXVzL3Nob3Avc3Vycm91bmQtc2V0LWJlYW0tZXJhLTEwMC1wYWlyIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiIxMGEwNzFiMy0zNTZiLTQ4MzItYWQyZC04OWM0MWJhY2IzNDEifQ&amp;signature=AQAAASSjjHo5m6dM2-Yfotym2FvBf9Gul_a0xtLbbKqlacyf&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sonos.com%2Fen-us%2Fshop%2Fsurround-set-beam-era-100-pair" class="rapid-with-clickid">带有 Beam 的环绕声套件</a>，其中包括 Beam 发声器和两个 Era 100 扬声器，价格不到 900 美元。考虑到 Era 100 和 Beam 是我们目前的<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-smart-speakers-151515264.html">智能扬声器</a>和条形音箱的首选，该套装将大大有助于升级您的客厅设置。</p><p><em>在 Twitter 上</em><em>关注</em><a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://twitter.com/EngadgetDeals"><em>@EngadgetDeals</em></a>并<a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://subscription.yahoo.net/Newsletter/Preference/sub?b=engadgetdeals&amp;src"><em>订阅 Engadget Deals 时事通讯，</em></a><em>了解最新的技术交易和购买建议。</em></p>本文最初出现在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/sonos-25-percent-off-fathers-day-sale-ends-this-weekend-120529289.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/sonos-25-percent-off-fathers-day-sale-end